 <name>Piece_Right</name>
 <summary>A validation framework for PHP</summary>
 <description>Piece_Right is a validation framework for PHP.
The following is a list of features of Piece_Right.
o Extensible validator system
o Extensible filter system
o A lot of built-in validators
o Another field watchers
o Pseudo fields
o Message variables
o Force validation
o YAML based configuration
o Dynamic configuration

The following is a list of built-in validators.
o Compare
o Date
o JapaneseDate
o Length
o List
o Range
o Regex
o WithMethod
 </description>
